## pip wrapper using Chinese mirror

pipzh ==  pip -i CHINESE_MIRROR



### install

```
pip install pipzh
```

### usage

```
pipzh install xxx
pipzh install xxx -s aliyun
```

**Notice**

pipzh == pips == pipcn, they are all the same

So Easy.

Enjoy Yourself.
